      <title>布林肯访问美国推动加沙停火的“最后机会”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/us-pushes-for-last-chance-of-gaza-ceasefire-as-blinken-visits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯将于周一抵达中东，加大力度推动加沙停火，这可能是说服以色列取消对南部城市拉法赫的袭击的最后机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/us-pushes-for-last-chance-of-gaza-ceasefire-as-blinken-visits</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 11:34:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰计划从七月起将公用事业电费削减五分之一</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/poland-aims-to-cut-utilities-power-tariffs-by-a-fifth-from-july</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰计划将公用事业公司征收的最高电价削减19%，以降低国家补贴成本，帮助家庭免受电价上涨的全面影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/poland-aims-to-cut-utilities-power-tariffs-by-a-fifth-from-july</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 10:34:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
